{
  "stem": "17.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 328.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was winter in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "The snow was laying on the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I didn't hurt myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And the train moved away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I laid down flat on the-- there were-- further there were some bushes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I laid flat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I decided to wait till it will get dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I don't know if I was thinking or that was instinct, I suppose, or whatever, destiny.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And probably about an hour, hour and a half, when it got dark, I saw a light at one spot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I was started to walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Of course, I put my-- pull out my Star of David that we were wearing all the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I walked towards the light.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And luckily, that was the street, that was the area, was opening to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "That was the gate to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And evening, people that work outside on the, on the labor camp, day laborers, were coming back home to sleep in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I approached the group.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I told them what happened, that I want to go back to the ghetto, if they can help me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And of course, you see, they are being counted every morning and evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "So-- but they gave me priority, and somebody else tried to sneak in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Because that was one head more than left in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So somehow, anyway, they protected me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They helped me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here I came back to the ghetto, where my-- Henry, and Sophie, and my aunt lived there also, my aunt, Irene Haber.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knew already that I, I was on this transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't count on me anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And here I come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was an unbelievable emotional scene.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was-- we were all getting out of our mind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was the final decision.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
